data.description: MOVE IN READY!!!!!! This home has so many updates, new flooring, freshly painted kitchen cabinets, new bathroom fixtures, new appliances, and fresh paint in some areas. The master bedroom/master bath is downstairs with a half bath close to the family room. Two dining areas, that are on each entrance of the kitchen that makes it easy for serving your guests. Large open patio for outdoor entertaining! Second two car garage can be used as a workshop or for extra parking. Park like private backyard to enjoy the birds and the wonderful shade trees.
